    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<strong>Save the Forest! Grow Powerful Spells!</strong><br><br>Embark on an enchanting pixel-art adventure as the last Floramancer, fighting to protect your beloved forest from ruthless robots. FloraMancer is a captivating action and farming game that combines the magic of spell-growing with thrilling battles against deforestation.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259300/extras/0d5c955d0e3f93061f7a594854ebc49f.avif?t=1758803956\" width=620 height=348 /></span><br><br>🌱 Grow &amp; Harvest: Plant seeds, nurture your garden, and cultivate stunning pixel art flowers. Each plant has unique preferences and growing them strategically will yield stronger and faster results. Protect your flowers from killer robots and the elements.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259300/extras/96585ae8176a7156cc5ea2292de7c753.avif?t=1758803956\" width=620 height=348 /></span><br><br>🌿 Spellbinding Powers: Harvest your plants to unlock potent spells and abilities. The more a plant grows and receives proper care, the more powerful the spells it will provide. Harness these abilities to find lost seeds, mine rocks, fight robots, and reclaim your forest.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259300/extras/14caf0899d6da2089690bf97ec412f95.avif?t=1758803956\" width=620 height=348 /></span><br><br>🔥 Elemental Mastery: From water to fire, air to earth, each plant-turned-spell offers distinct powers. Water can douse flames and shock enemies, air deflects bullets and aids in growing fire plants, earth shoots fast-moving spikes and can mine through rocks, and fire clears paths through obstacles and much more!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259300/extras/da7dac6699176b4ebf817349e8f237b5.avif?t=1758803956\" width=620 height=348 /></span><br><br>🌺 The Last Floramancer: Take on the role of the sole Floramancer and lead the charge against the robots, who are relentlessly exploiting your forest's resources. Reclaim your home, one spell at a time.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259300/extras/28b010983cef8451e985beab2e53a4eb.avif?t=1758803956\" width=620 height=348 /></span><br><br>🤖 Tactical Enemies: Battle squads of robots, each with their own behaviors and vulnerabilities. Learn their weaknesses and devise effective strategies to overcome them.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259300/extras/cfb8432d11c404d3c66a5fcc3fd11857.avif?t=1758803956\" width=620 height=348 /></span><br><br><br>💀 Consequences of Death: In the afterworld, choose one of three doors to return, but beware of the small punishments they carry, such as losing seeds, spells, or spell slots.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259300/extras/7f76cebf566f00acf8c580dfa0cf26ba.avif?t=1758803956\" width=620 height=348 /></span>",
